  "mainText": "Italiano English Reserved Area Contacts Company Pens Customisation Sample kits Finishes Recycled pens More maxema ® via vittime delle foibe 15 10088 volpiano torino italy t +39 011 970 4500 f +39 011 970 4550 maxema@maxema.com P PRODUCTS Our pens Kind / Kind / Icon Pure / Flow Pure / Dot / Zink / Pixel / Bay / Mood Metal / Kind / Mood / Flow / View / Tag Green / Next / Tag / Icon / Icon green / Ethic Search by color rose/purple azure / blue green yellow/orange red cream/brown grey black white select a color S Services customisation packaging pantone colors sample kits C COMPANY Maxema Company contacts FAVORITES SAMPLE KITS ACCOUNT FAQ MEDIA DISCLAIMER previous model/ next model HomePens Catalogue Tag Tag imposing elegance Technical information Download pdfof this model A pen designed as a tribute to perfect, frill-free elegance. Rigorous styling embellished by the softer lines of the clip and gently curved closing plug which is the distinctive trait of the Tag. A skilful combination of lithe, sinuous shapes and rigour that is pleasing to the eye and to the touch. Available in recycled plastic for orders over 10,000 units. 1/4 Details 2/4 Variants 3/4 Technical information 4/4 Customisations log in P/Tag 1/4 Details Details of the pen Elegance and linearity to express all the strength of a brand Its rigorous styling is softened by the smooth curve of the clip and closing plug Rubber finish barrel: popular because it is good to look at and pleasant to touch 2/4 Models and colors Available in 5 models and 54 color variants TA1 - MATT AL B Show details add to favorites ABS plastic, matt finishes, coloured closing plug, solid white barrel and clip, aluminium painted tip TA1 - B CR Show details add to favorites ABS plastic, glossy finishes, solid colours, chromed tip and coloured barrel TA1 - C CR Show details add to favorites ABS plastic, glossy finishes, solid colours, chromed parts TA1 - MET AL Show details add to favorites ABS plastic, metallic painting, coloured barrel and cap, parts painted in aluminium TA1 - AL CR Show details add to favorites ABS plastic, aluminium painting, chromed parts 3/4 Technical information Print areas and tech specs Features ● twist-action ● made of non-toxic, highly resistant ABS plastic ● galvanic process used to chrome tip and upper plug ● Jumbo Refill, blue and black ink ● available in glossy, matt, rubberised and metallic or aluminium painted finish Modularity you can combine differently coloured parts from the same version (or code number), or elements from different versions A plug B clip C barrel D tip Print areas 1 pad printing 47 x 9 mm 2 pad printing 40 x 9 mm 3 screen printing 42 x 30 mm 4 pad printing 8 x 10 mm 4/4 Customisations The brands mentioned in this catalogue are the exclusive property of the respective owners. They are used for purely illustrative purposes and cannot be the object of any buying and selling transactions, under any circumstances. via vittime delle foibe 15 10088 volpiano torino italy t +39 011 970 4500 f +39 011 970 4550 maxema@maxema.com MAXEMA SRL P.IVA 05321380015 privacy policy var acceptText='Accetto'; var policy_url='/cookie_privacy_policy/en'; var cookie_message='Il sito www.maxema.com utilizza cookie esclusivamente tecnici per permettere una corretta navigazione e la completa fruizione di tutti i contenuti da parte dell\\'utente. Non utilizziamo in alcun modo cookie di profilazione.'; var acceptText='I Understand'; var policy_url='/cookie_privacy_policy/en'; var cookie_message='This site uses cookies to improve their services and experience of readers. If you decide to continue browsing we consider that you accept their use.'; $(document).ready(function(){ $.cookieBar({ message: cookie_message, acceptButton: true, acceptText: acceptText, policyButton: true, policyText: 'Privacy Policy', policyURL: policy_url, autoEnable: true, acceptOnContinue: false, acceptOnScroll: false, acceptAnyClick: false, expireDays: 365, renewOnVisit: false, forceS